    public class MultiHubPaginator
extends Paginator<MultiHubPaginator.MultiRedditId>
    This is specially designed to iterate /r/multihub and pick out information about multireddits submitted there.

    • Field Detail

      • MULTIREDDIT_URL_REGEX

        public static final java.lang.String MULTIREDDIT_URL_REGEX
        Matches a multireddit URL. See here for a demonstration, and here for a list of URLs to test on

        Usernames must only contain alphanumeric characters, underscores, and hyphens with a max length of 20 (source).

        Multireddits must only contain alphanumeric characters, underscores, and hyphens, and have a max length of 21 (source)
